title: IG Report, Impeachment & USMCA
itunes:title: IG Report, Impeachment & USMCA
description:
Kevin spoke with George Seay, CEO of Annandale Capital and Kevin Walling, Democratic Strategist at HG Creative Media. They discussed the IG report, impeachment and USMCA.

Congressman Chris Stewart, R-Utah also called in to discuss the Fairness for All Act and impeachment.
